subject: tizen.org synchronization with tizendev.org - add missing license file
commitMessage:
tizen.org synchronization with tizendev.org - add missing license file

%license macro has been used to install LICENSE file.

Add license file and NOTICE file into rpm package

License file must be included in Tizen SDK release binary
because Tizen SDK license is deleted.

Change-Id: I2c82d31a19f1242ca321d4c8903c4d6aeb811526
Signed-off-by: Jae-young Hwang <j-zero.hwang@samsung.com>
Signed-off-by: Jacek Pielaszkiewicz <j.pielaszkie@samsung.com>
